reviewText: I AM A BIG JOHN MAYALL AND AS I MEET HIM BEFORE AND AFTER A SHOW IN DUNEDIN NZ IN APRIL 2010 WHERE WE HAD A GOOD CHAT ABOUT HIS LIFE IN MUSIC HE ALSO SINGED QUITE A FEW RECORDS AND OTHER THINGS THAT I HAD WITH ME,HE TOLD ME ABOUT THIS DVD SO I SO GLAD I FOUND IT .THANK YOU.REGARDS ANDREW IN NEW ZEALAND
